'''选举计数法'''（Electoral Count Act）是一部1887年通過的美国联邦法律，這部法律规定了[[美国总统选举|美国总统选举]]后[[美国国会|美国国会]]计算[[选举人票|选举人票]]的程序<ref>{{Cite web|title=Positive Law Codification|url=https://uscode.house.gov/codification/legislation.shtml|accessdate=2021-01-02|author=|date=|first=|work=uscode.house.gov|publisher=[[Office_of_the_Law_Revision_Counsel|Office of the Law Revision Counsel]]|archiveurl=|archivedate=}}</ref>。該法出台背景是[[1876年美國總統選舉|1876年美國總統選舉]]中美國的幾個州提交了有爭議的選民名單，且當時分裂的國會在幾個星期內都無法解決僵局<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Counting Electoral Votes: An Overview of Procedures at the Joint Session, Including Objections by Members of Congress|url=https://fas.org/sgp/crs/misc/RL32717.pdf|accessdate=22 December 2020|author=Rybicki|date=|first=Elizabeth|work=[[Congressional_Research_Service|Congressional Research Service]]|publisher=Congressional Research Service|archiveurl=|archivedate=}}</ref>。

该法旨在尽量减少国会对选举争端的参与，而将解决争端的主要责任交给各州。该法规定了各州在解决争端、核证选举结果和将选举结果送交国会时应遵循的程序和最后期限<ref name=":1">{{Cite book|last=Foley|first=Edward|url=https://www.worldcat.org/oclc/928386780|title=Ballot battles : the history of disputed elections in the United States|publisher=[[Oxford_University_Press|Oxford University Press]]|year=2016|isbn=978-0-19-023528-4|location=New York|pages=153|lccn=2015025434|oclc=928386780|authorlink=Edward B. Foley}}</ref><ref name=":0" />。

